# Minimal cube mesh for mock / saved-RGB-D pipeline testing.
# Edge length = 0.05 m, centered at the origin (object frame center).
# UNITS: METERS (FoundationPose assumes metric model coordinates).
# Half-extent = 0.025 m on each axis.
#
# 8 vertices, 12 triangular faces. Normals are computed by the mesh loader
# (trimesh) from the geometry.
v -0.025 -0.025 -0.025
v  0.025 -0.025 -0.025
v  0.025  0.025 -0.025
v -0.025  0.025 -0.025
v -0.025 -0.025  0.025
v  0.025 -0.025  0.025
v  0.025  0.025  0.025
v -0.025  0.025  0.025
# faces (CCW), 1-indexed
f 1 2 3
f 1 3 4
f 5 7 6
f 5 8 7
f 1 5 6
f 1 6 2
f 2 6 7
f 2 7 3
f 3 7 8
f 3 8 4
f 4 8 5
f 4 5 1
